===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[precious]] or [[semi-]][[precious]] stone; [[gem]], [[gemstone]].
# A valuable object used for personal ornamentation, especially one made of precious metals and stones; a [[piece]] of [[jewellery]].
#* Shakespeare
#*: Plate of rare device, and '''jewels''' / Of rich and exquisite form.
# {{context|figuratively|lang=en}} Anything considered precious or valuable.
#: ''Galveston was the '''jewel''' of Texas prior to the hurricane.''
# A [[bearing]] for a [[pivot]] in a [[watch]], formed of a crystal or precious stone.

